Class DeckModel

    edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.Model

    public class DeckModel
extends edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.AbstractModel
    This class is meant to represent a deck of cards that the user can pick from for making estimates to a game.

    1.0

      • canAllowsMultipleSelection

        public boolean canAllowsMultipleSelection()
        Gets whether multiple card selection is allowed for this deck. This means that the user can select mutiple cards from the deck and sum their values to make their estimate.
